  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897390/extras/5c9d07e2bc09cfb876e08814c205f105.avif?t=1643377455\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br>The city is full of enemy robot patrol and needs someone to protect it. You are the last hope, the last chance to survive… <br><br>Fly all over the city and fight against cyborg invasion. Your goal is to hold out as long as possible and become the mightiest robot. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find attacker and kill him to unlock new robot defenders: each robot has its' own weapon and force. <br></li><li>Never stop: play the infinite game and try to hold out.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897390/extras/75d1159f868432806ebe7b65fa925c2c.avif?t=1643377455\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 types of robot defenders;<br></li><li>2 types of powerful weapon;<br></li><li>some types of enemies, which are coming in waves and become stronger.</li></ul>",
